data.title: Willie Nelson’s 4th of July Picnic is coming to Philly for the first time ever! Join Willie and his friends on Independence Day in the...
data.meta_description:
williesreserveofficial on March 26, 2024: "Willie Nelson’s 4th of July Picnic is coming to Philly for the first time ever! Join Willie and his friends on Independence Day in the birthplace of America, with @bobdylan, @robertplantofficial & @alisonkrauss, @marenmorris, @mavisstaples, and @celissemusic. Tickets available to the public Friday, 3/29 at 10am ET.

July 4 | @freedommortgagepavilion in Camden, NJ
Tickets at willienelson.com
#williespicnic @blackbird_presents".
